* In {{ill|Tenmon|ja|е§©жЦЗ}} 6 (1537 AD), the temple founded in Tsushima by {{ill|Kagetetsu Gensu|ja|жЩѓиљНзОДиШЗ}} was named "Itou" (йЕК) by combining the characters of Teiyuu.

==Yin Fire Rooster (дЄБйЕЙ)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|и•њжЪ¶}} year whose final digit is 1 or 6 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|еНБеє≤}} are {{ill|Sin|ja|иЊЫ}} and {{ill|Bing|ja|дЄЩ}}), the month of {{ill|August|ja|8жЬИ}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|жЬИ (жЪ¶)}} of {{ill|Teiyuu|ja|дЄБйЕЙ}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Old Calendar|ja|жЧІжЪ¶}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|зѓАжЬИ}} (from {{ill|White Dew|ja|зЩљйЬ≤}} until the day before {{ill|Cold Dew|ja|еѓТйЬ≤}}) as applicable.

