* In {{ill|Keich≈Н|ja|жЕґйХЈ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keich≈Н|qq=}} 2 (1597 AD), the campaign known as the {{ill|Keich≈Н Campaign|ja|жЦЗз¶ДгГїжЕґйХЈгБЃељє#жЕґйХЈгБЃељє|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keich≈Н Campaign|qq=}} took place, which in Korea is referred to as the "Teiyuu Rebellion."
