==Yin Fire Rooster (дЄБйЕЙ)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|и•њжЪ¶|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=и•њжЪ¶|4=zh|5=еЕђеЕГ|6=es|7=Era com√Їn|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Western calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=}} year whose final digit is 1 or 6 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|еНБеє≤|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} are {{ill|Sin|ja|иЊЫ|1=Kanoto (иЊЫ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (иЊЫ)|qq=}} and {{ill|Bing|ja|дЄЩ|1=Hinoe (дЄЩ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bing|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (дЄЩ)|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|August|ja|8жЬИ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/August|qq=}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|жЬИ (жЪ¶)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/month (calendar)|qq=}} of {{ill|Teiyuu|ja|1=Yin Fire Rooster|2=ja|дЄБйЕЙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teiyuu|qq=}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|жЧІжЪ¶|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|зѓАжЬИ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Seasonal Month|qq=}} (from {{ill|White Dew|ja|зЩљйЬ≤|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/White Dew|qq=}} until the day before {{ill|Cold Dew|ja|еѓТйЬ≤|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Cold Dew|qq=}}) as applicable.

