{{infobox Chinese|l=Yin Fire Rooster|kanji=дЄБйЕЙ|romaji=hinoto tori|onyomi=teiy≈Ђ|p=dƒЂy«Тu|w=ting-yu|mi=t ∞i≈ЛвБµ¬≥ iћѓ…§ Кћѓ¬≤¬є|y=deng1 jau5|j=deng1 jau5|ci=t…Ы≈Л j…Рu|mc=t√¶≈Л j…®u|oc-bs=t√¶≈Л j…ѓ Ф|qq=}}
{{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=}}
'''Yang Fire Rooster also known as дЄБйЕЙ''' (hinototori, teika no tori, teiyuu) is one of the elements of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|еЕ≠еНБеє≤жФѓ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}.

It is the 34th combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|еЕ≠еНБеє≤жФѓ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}, preceded by {{ill|Bingshen|ja|1=Yang Fire Monkey|2=ja|дЄЩзФ≥|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bingshen|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Wuxu|ja|1=Yang Earth Dog|2=ja|жИКжИМ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wuxu|qq=}}. In the framework of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|йЩ∞йЩљдЇФи°МжАЭжГ≥|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|еНБеє≤|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Tei|ja|дЄБ|1=Hinoto (дЄБ)|lt=Hinoto (дЄБ)|2=ja|3=дЄБ|4=zh|5=дЄБ|1=Hinoto (дЄБ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tei|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoto (дЄБ)|qq=}} represents yin {{ill|Fire|ja|зБЂ|1=Fire (wuxing)|lt=Fire (зБЂ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fire|qq=}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|еНБдЇМжФѓ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branches|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Rooster|ja|йЕЙ|1=Rooster (Zodiac)|lt=Rooster (йЕЙ)|2=ja|3=йЕЙ|1=Rooster (zodiac)|2=ja|3=йЕЙ|4=fr|5=Coq (astrologie chinoise)|6=nl|7=Haan (astrologie)|lt=Rooster (йЕЙ)|1=Rooster (zodiac)|lt=Rooster (йЕЙ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rooster|13=User:Immanuelle/Rooster (zodiac)|qq=}} represents yin {{ill|Metal|ja|Metal (йЗС)|1=Metal (wuxing)|lt=Metal (йЗС)|2=es|3=Metal (Wu Xing)|4=it|5=Metallo (elemento)|6=vi|7=Kim (Ng≈© h√†nh)|8=tr|9=Metal (klasik element)|10=uk|11=–Ь–µ—В–∞–ї (–£-—Б—Ц–љ)|1=Metal (wuxing)|lt=Metal (йЗС)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Metal|qq=}}, establishing a restraining relationship ({{ill|Mutual Restraint|ja|дЇФи°МжАЭжГ≥#зЫЄеЙЛпЉИгБЭгБЖгБУгБПпЉЙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Restraint|qq=}}) (i.e. Fire overcomes Metal).

