==Pronunciation== PronounceYin Fire Rooster
==Years of Yin Fire Rooster== A year in the [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] that leaves a remainder of 37 when divided by 60 is a [[:en:Year|year]] of {{ill|Teiyuu|ja|1=Yin Fire Rooster|2=ja|дЄБйЕЙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teiyuu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teiyuu|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Fire Rooster|qq=}}. {| class="wikitable" |+'''Yin Fire Rooster (дЄБйЕЙ)'s years table''' |- ! [[:en:1st millennium|1st Millennium]] !! [[:en:2nd millennium|2nd Millennium]] !! [[:en:3rd millennium|3rd Millennium]] |- | * [[:en:AD 37|37 AD]] * [[:en:AD 97|97 AD]] * [[:en:157|157 AD]] * [[:en:217|217 AD]] * [[:en:277|277 AD]] * [[:en:337|337 AD]] * [[:en:397|397 AD]] * [[:en:457|457 AD]] * [[:en:517|517 AD]] * [[:en:577|577 AD]] * [[:en:637|637 AD]] * [[:en:697|697 AD]] * [[:en:AD 757|757 AD]] * [[:en:817|817 AD]] * [[:en:877|877 AD]] * [[:en:937|937 AD]] * [[:en:997|997 AD]] | * [[:en:1057|1057 AD]] * [[:en:1117|1117 AD]] * [[:en:1177|1177 AD]] * [[:en:1237|1237 AD]] * [[:en:1297|1297 AD]] * [[:en:1357|1357 AD]] * [[:en:1417|1417 AD]] * [[:en:1477|1477 AD]] * [[:en:1537|1537 AD]] * [[:en:1597|1597 AD]] * [[:en:1657|1657 AD]] * [[:en:1717|1717 AD]] * [[:en:1777|1777 AD]] * [[:en:1837|1837 AD]] * [[:en:1897|1897 AD]] * [[:en:1957|1957 AD]] | * [[:en:2017|2017 AD]] * {{ill|2077 AD|ja|2077еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2077|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2077 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2137 AD|ja|2137еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2137|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2137 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2197 AD|ja|2197еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2197|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2197 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2257 AD|ja|2257еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2257|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2257 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2317 AD|ja|2317еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2317|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2317 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2377 AD|ja|2377еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2377|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2377 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2437 AD|ja|2437еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2437|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2437 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2497 AD|ja|2497еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2497|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2497 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2557 AD|ja|2557еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2557|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2557 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2617 AD|ja|2617еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2617|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2617 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2677 AD|ja|2677еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2677|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2677 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2737 AD|ja|2737еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2737|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2737 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2797 AD|ja|2797еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2797|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2797 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2857 AD|ja|2857еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2857|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2857 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2917 AD|ja|2917еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2917|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2917 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2977 AD|ja|2977еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2977|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2977 AD|qq=}} |}
=== Events === * In [[:en:Keich≈Н|Keich≈Н]] 2 (1597 AD), the campaign known as the {{ill|Keich≈Н Campaign|ja|жЦЗз¶ДгГїжЕґйХЈгБЃељє#жЕґйХЈгБЃељє|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keich≈Н Campaign|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keich≈Н Campaign|qq=}} took place, which in Korea is referred to as the "Teiyuu Rebellion." * In {{ill|Tenmon|ja|е§©жЦЗ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenmon|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenmon|qq=}} 6 (1537 AD), the temple founded in Tsushima by {{ill|Kagetetsu Gensu|ja|жЩѓиљНзОДиШЗ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kagetetsu Gensu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kagetetsu Gensu|qq=}} was named "Itou" (йЕК) by combining the characters of Teiyuu.
==Months of Yin Fire Rooster== In a [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] year whose final digit is 1 or 6 (when the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stems]] are {{ill|Sin|ja|иЊЫ|1=Kanoto (иЊЫ)|lt=Kanoto (иЊЫ)|2=ja|3=иЊЫ|4=zh|5=иЊЫ|1=Kanoto (иЊЫ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (иЊЫ)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (иЊЫ)|qq=}} and {{ill|Bing|ja|дЄЩ|1=Hinoe (дЄЩ)|lt=Hinoe (дЄЩ)|2=ja|3=дЄЩ|4=zh|5=дЄЩ|1=Hinoe (дЄЩ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bing|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (дЄЩ)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bing|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (дЄЩ)|qq=}}), the month of [[:en:August|August]] is designated as the [[:en:Month|month (calendar)]] of {{ill|Teiyuu|ja|1=Yin Fire Rooster|2=ja|дЄБйЕЙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teiyuu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teiyuu|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Fire Rooster|qq=}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|жЧІжЪ¶|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the [[:en:Solar term|Solar term]] (from [[:en:Bailu (solar term)|White Dew]] until the day before [[:en:Hanlu|Cold Dew]]) as applicable.
==Days of Yin Fire Rooster== The {{ill|selected day|ja|йБЄжЧ•|1=Senjitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=}} for {{ill|Teiyuu|ja|1=Yin Fire Rooster|2=ja|дЄБйЕЙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teiyuu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teiyuu|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Fire Rooster|qq=}} is as follows. === йБЄжЧ• === The day of {{ill|Teiyuu|ja|1=Yin Fire Rooster|2=ja|дЄБйЕЙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teiyuu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teiyuu|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Fire Rooster|qq=}} is the 5th day of {{ill|Ten Ten Ichij≈Н|ja|е§©дЄАе§©дЄК|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ten Ten Ichij≈Н|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ten Ten Ichij≈Н|qq=}}.
